import React from 'react';
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom';
import {
  Container,
  Box,
  Typography,
  Button,
  Paper,
  Grid,
} from '@mui/material';
import PeopleIcon from '@mui/icons-material/People';
import ChatIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Chat';
import ShareIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Share';

function Home() {
  return (
    <Box
      sx={{
        minHeight: '80vh',
        display: 'flex',
        flexDirection: 'column',
        justifyContent: 'center',
      }}
    >
      <Container maxWidth="lg">
        <Grid container spacing={4} alignItems="center">
          <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
            <Typography
              variant="h2"
              component="h1"
              gutterBottom
              sx={{ fontWeight: 700, color: 'primary.main' }}
            >
              Connect with friends and share your moments
            </Typography>
            <Typography variant="h5" color="text.secondary" paragraph>
              Join our social media platform to stay connected with friends, share your stories,
              and discover amazing content from people around the world.
            </Typography>
            <Box sx={{ mt: 4, display: 'flex', gap: 2 }}>
              <Button
                component={Link}
                to="/register"
                variant="contained"
                size="large"
                sx={{ px: 4 }}
              >
                Get Started
              </Button>
              <Button
                component={Link}
                to="/login"
                variant="outlined"
                size="large"
                sx={{ px: 4 }}
              >
                Sign In
              </Button>
            </Box>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
            <Grid container spacing={2}>
              <Grid item xs={12}>
                <Paper
                  elevation={0}
                  sx={{
                    p: 3,
                    bgcolor: 'primary.light',
                    color: 'white',
                    borderRadius: 2,
                  }}
                >
                  <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', gap: 2 }}>
                    <PeopleIcon fontSize="large" />
                    <Box>
                      <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
                        Connect with Friends
                      </Typography>
                      <Typography variant="body2">
                        Find and connect with friends, family, and like-minded people.
                      </Typography>
                    </Box>
                  </Box>
                </Paper>
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={12}>
                <Paper
                  elevation={0}
                  sx={{
                    p: 3,
                    bgcolor: 'secondary.light',
                    color: 'white',
                    borderRadius: 2,
                  }}
                >
                  <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', gap: 2 }}>
                    <ChatIcon fontSize="large" />
                    <Box>
                      <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
                        Share Your Thoughts
                      </Typography>
                      <Typography variant="body2">
                        Express yourself and engage in meaningful conversations.
                      </Typography>
                    </Box>
                  </Box>
                </Paper>
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={12}>
                <Paper
                  elevation={0}
                  sx={{
                    p: 3,
                    bgcolor: 'success.light',
                    color: 'white',
                    borderRadius: 2,
                  }}
                >
                  <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', gap: 2 }}>
                    <ShareIcon fontSize="large" />
                    <Box>
                      <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
                        Share Your World
                      </Typography>
                      <Typography variant="body2">
                        Share photos, videos, and stories with your network.
                      </Typography>
                    </Box>
                  </Box>
                </Paper>
              </Grid>
            </Grid>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
      </Container>
    </Box>
  );
}

export default Home;
